<title>LOOK AND THOU SHALT LIVE!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Enin, Kalvari-a Hukdampa,
 Enin nang leh kei di'n A thawkna;
 Lungsieta A hun sapna ngaiin,
 &quot;Enin, hing inla&quot;!

[V2]
 Enin hing inla,
 Enin hing inla!
 Nang dinga A thihna Kross enin,
 Enin, hing inla!

[V3]
 2. Tha gikpuok hukdam ding na nei em?
 Kum khawsawt hinna neih na nuom em?
 Isu ngeiin tatna A pie tai,
 Enin, hing inla!

[V4]
 3. Enin, thana thokit Hukdampa,
 Kinin, zuonin mun a um lai hin;
 A nuih melin lungkham nawhmang ding,
 Enin, hing inla!

[V5]
 4. Isu vana um ei gensak di'n,
 Gilo hatlote taksap A hei!
 Thawn loin na kalsuon pui ina,
 Enin, hing inla!</lyrics>
</song>